Ubercart Gift Wrap Module
---------------------------
This module is a simple port to Drupal 6 of the Ubercart Gift Wrap module available at http://www.ubercart.org/contrib/7057. Thanks to hvitebjorn (http://www.ubercart.org/user/2974) for creating this module.

The port is based on the 2/11/2009 version of code released on the Ubercart website.

Installation
---------------------------
Do the standard Drupal installation steps:
* Download the code into the modules/ubercart/ folder
* Enable the module
* Go to the Store Checkout configuration page (admin/store/settings/checkout). You should see a Gift Wrap Settings tab.
* Set the price per gift-wrap, and also if the wrap-job is on a per-item or per-order basis


